Subject: drm/fb-helper: Remove drm_fb_helper_fbdev_{setup, teardown}()
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 8204f235a64e175b624893f91531a9ba76dcc8e5
Patch-mainline: v5.6-rc1
References: jsc#SLE-12680, jsc#SLE-12880, jsc#SLE-12882, jsc#SLE-12883, jsc#SLE-13496, jsc#SLE-15322

Both functions are unused and can be removed. Drivers should use
drm_fbdev_generic_setup() instead.

Signed-off-by: Thomas Zimmermann <tzimmermann@suse.de>
Reviewed-by: Noralf Tr√∏nnes <noralf@tronnes.org>
